Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:31.72,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}希望！だってあなたと言う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:34.89,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}トキメキに出会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:39.29,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}約束だよずっとBe with you
