Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:27.51,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}但愿相约于地球之上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:34.89,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}因为邂逅的正是这个使我悸动的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:39.29,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}约好了哦永远Be with you
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小寻啊  我是妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我40秒后到家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年  你脸色苍白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着慢着慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是好事…当然是好事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么解释这俩家伙的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「是她俩硬要住在这里的」这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈真的会相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我对少年你没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄个不好就可能被贴上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「父母不在期间带女生回家」的标签
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这样盯着会怀孕的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌～讨厌～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这不公正的对待表示抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧  宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们又擅自闯进来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻  大白天的就好大胆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  再激烈点！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}少年  你居然敢袭击奈亚子  胆子不小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈…哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个误会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是你想象中的那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一直微笑着潜行在您儿子身边的混沌——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚拉托提普
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚拉托提普？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了怀上真寻的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未来…更正  是从星之国度千里迢迢而来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把我当成儿媳妇  叫我奈亚子就行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿媳妇你个头！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的妈妈  初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是奈亚子的妻子克图格亚  可以叫我克子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子你个头！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我是丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲自生孩子或者让你生都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脑子里装的是花园牧场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮不到你说！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜行的混沌和克图格亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到她当时随口乱扯的话竟会真的成为伏线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}这傲娇和叉子PLAY都是源于\N曾记载在禁忌黑之书中的被诅咒的邪神猎人的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到真寻身上也留有这种血！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我也没想到会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小寻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧离开她俩身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…慢着妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然会在自己家里遇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我们呢…非但没袭击您儿子…而且还救过他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  小寻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样  好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  不是的…这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子好像人畜无害的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看它的眼神就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…夏塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然比你的主人我先得到母亲大人的宠爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的宠物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是  而且拥有一双可爱眼睛的我  别说人畜无害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还担任着真寻的护卫一职
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小寻的护卫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我详细说下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要爆发全面战争了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此回必将其彻彻底底剥夺殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3c7A2BE3\shad0\fscx75\bord6}Mother's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3cFFFFFF\shad0\fscx75}Mother's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星保护机构
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的娱乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大致上明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这母子的拥抱到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在补充釨元素
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釨元素？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可以轮到妈妈来说明一下状况了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊  妈妈在做邪神猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？邪神猎人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打猎了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编写这本书的就是妈妈大学时代研究会的教授
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  妈妈受到这位教授的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔帮助他一起狩猎邪神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是爸爸知道这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  夫妻之间没有什么可隐瞒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然包容妻子打零工  真是体贴的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也正是喜欢他这点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的父母  好恩爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(331,323)\fs20}lovelove
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来恩爱一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话  love后面会跟着克拉夫特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：克苏鲁神话作者洛夫克拉夫特的梗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子  和我来亲亲爱爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让即将诞生的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承我们的装备与能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我死了你都别想！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢         
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}放开我  克子  随便去找个夜魇交尾去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我想和奈亚子交尾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}给我差不多一点啊  你这个变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}和奈亚子在一起  疼痛都让我感觉好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你还有气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真是个难缠的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一起回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  爸爸这次也是很勉强才获得了假期
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了弥补  这段时间估计会住在公司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是邪神猎人  但也没有做很危险的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一份零工而已  别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是份零工啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…奈亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是我太武断了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里…完全没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  真是好孩子呢  奈亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始出发捕获目标人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的霸权  终将落入我们的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为也许还会有敌人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会继续保护真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的工作是不是该到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…我们还有保护地球幻梦境的重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能继续将此处作为据点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  妈妈  肯定不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  留她俩在这儿也没什么大问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么轻易地决定真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她俩不止眼神  各方面来讲都很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她们在保护地球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定得帮助她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是母亲大人  真明白事理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就是说我正式成为八坂家的新娘了  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  奈亚子喜欢小寻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES！我无比认真地深爱着真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果是作为「新娘」  就有点无法认同了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我希望小寻能过更普通的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以和奈亚子结为恋人或夫妻这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该更慎重的考虑一下  就是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是借宿很欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也要和小寻一直做朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SAN值正在持续下降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来进入期待已久的礼物时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次的礼品是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又买这些老式的游戏机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为啊  买这些东西时会有种为逝去的美好记忆买单的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢打游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们会很谈得来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要赶紧玩玩看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  妈妈肚子也饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想吃小寻做的晚饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想吃哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大份的釨元素哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我多放蔬菜大蒜和油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  该做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你也在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得烹饪时共同作业会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古话说的好  奇迹总会在邂逅到最棒的搭档时触发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是不想让你进厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么绝情的言词…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道你会用什么材料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确至今为止也许是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(274,323)\fs20}邪神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是「人」是会长进的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那给我解释一下你手里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是宇宙知名品牌的肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎布·尼古拉丝牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：莎布·尼古拉丝为克苏鲁神话中的外神之一\N其形象为黑云般的巨大肉块  有着许多触手  以及滴着黏液的大嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孕育千万子孙的森之黑山羊 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：出自洛夫克拉夫特  《暗夜呢喃》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑  我刚才应该全扔了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想为你和母亲大人献上一餐美味的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的食材仅限地球产
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激万分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子定当竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐周年庆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  克子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和母亲大人在讨论游戏经
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  宇宙也有游戏机的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  X-oth和HS3平分市场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是觉得地球的游戏机比较受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  我丢个音爆弹咯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是真寻  真有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是「YES·NO抱枕」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放马过来吧  真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦讨厌啦  这也是喜欢的一种表现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果两边都是YES啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做好了随时接受真寻的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子周边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又软又滑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  克子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩给我收敛点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨间釨元素
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你们俩  不可以打架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不给我收手  当心我揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍人得做好挨揍的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵  正好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战翻别人可不是什么难事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过不可以打架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人！请冷静！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是乖孩子！没有打架！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻  我先走了  前面等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为妈妈回来  就可以回到过去的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似情况更糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？站得起来不？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  有没有哪疼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有受伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没摔倒  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  我也在想心事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那互相扯平啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦  是个善良的大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善良的大哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不后悔么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己选择的道路  义无反顾！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在大庭广众之下犯傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  早上起就累了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来才知道八坂同学有两个同龄的亲戚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非还有其他不认识的亲戚？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子  后来和八坂怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿  没有进展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么腼腆的真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会冷不防地推倒我  向造孩子发展…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠绪  有没有让奈亚子整晚淫欲肆意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热血沸腾的作战？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克子闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…珠绪  怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  男友攻陷法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…这个怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力挤  强调胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一阵恶寒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻  午饭吃热狗怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说看这东西的正式名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廷达洛斯之猎犬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去时间的棱角里一头撞死啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eroba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也擅长做三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且问你一下  究竟是什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邓尼奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用勉强装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人说的釨元素到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似地球上的元素周期表没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个妈妈随口扯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号称缺乏它会倍感寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了克子  你在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月的少年blood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？也给我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年blood？好像休刊了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大概第7期的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的出版社买断了它  让它复刊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球也常见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本以外的地区畅销的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超前的游戏机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的道理啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球以外  就能畅销的杂志啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的话已经先回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:18:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上的大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到又能见面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  原来你在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是根本找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没来过这种店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有点怕怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  让你陪我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我也正好肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这里偶遇！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我和真寻被命运的红线系在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  跟踪我来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得这么难听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极混沌的中心  在我耳边低语道「多买点」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  居然会上赠品的钩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子和克子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  莲太老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：莲太为昵称  与哈斯塔同音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来这孩子也是宇宙人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈斯塔…难道是风属性的最高位的邪神！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老弟…也就是说他是男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和莲太从宇宙幼儿园时起就一直同校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙小学的时候莲太还是年级委员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为可以事事加上宇宙二字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公务员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁饭碗  真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}明明只是个家里蹲  靠着关系给当上了公务员  那的确是赢家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲太为什么来地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来是啊  你不是曾在贺年卡上说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在塞莱诺的图书馆做图书管理员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这贺年卡内容真传统啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸最近说要我帮他工作的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是才辞了图书馆的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲太爸爸在做什么工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说在找人就是在帮令尊的忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  应该住在这附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我路痴…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住址呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有户主的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  这家人姓八坂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找的人的名字叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  八坂赖子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…我妈妈
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的婚礼已经指日可待了  真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪张嘴在说这种胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可爱的嘴唇啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.87,0:23:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给人的第一印象可是糟透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破这种恶劣情况的秘策终于发动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话「伟大的X的阴谋」  Let's go！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.42,0:23:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你闭嘴啦！


